<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Support Ticket Confirmation</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: #f6d4e8;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #ae2d68;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-logo {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        width: 100px;
        max-width: 150px;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 28px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .email-body h2 {
        color: #333333;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin: 10px 0 20px;
      }

      .email-body p {
        color: #1e1e1e;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .ticket-box {
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .ticket-box p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #333;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #ae2d68;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Support Ticket Confirmation</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Logo -->
      <img
        src="http://localhost:3333/images/Logoabby.png"
        alt="Abby n Bev Logo"
        class="email-logo"
      />

      <!-- Body -->
      <div class="email-body">
        <h2>Hi, {{ name }}</h2>
        <p>Terima kasih telah menghubungi <b>Abby n Bev</b>. Kami sudah menerima laporan kamu dengan detail sebagai berikut:</p>

        <div class="ticket-box">
          <p><b>Subjek:</b> {{ subject }}</p>
          <p><b>Pesan:</b> {{ message }}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Tim kami akan segera meninjau laporanmu dan memberikan update secepat mungkin. üôè</p>
        <p>Salam hangat,<br /><b>Tim Support Abby n Bev</b></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ currentYear }} CV. Gaya Beauty Utama, All Rights Reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
